{"tid":99608,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論+微劇透影評] 神奇虎爸 獸父 野外 群P 手指 少年","createTime":"2017-01-29T10:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T14:54:03.000Z","uid":66182,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15926abe4b2f84924a67e4ad2f16bf543db97b64","tid":99608,"uid":66182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T10:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/183637_15949c97759dfc1e788e235cf0f5a8cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F183637_15949c97759dfc1e788e235cf0f5a8cd.jpg&h=6c454636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n神奇虎爸 Captain Fantastic<br />\n<br />\n故事概要:<br />\n虎爸Ben與妻子Leslie誕下6名子女後決定要在荒山野嶺以有別於公共教育制度的方式育子成為抗拒資本主義又能在野外獨立求生的新人類。虎爸凡事以「求真相、拒蒙騙」的宗旨中立地向子女傳遞資訊，包括直接告知幼女什麼是性交及母親精神病發自殺身亡。每天過著打獵、種植、體能訓練及閱讀學習的生活，每名子女居然都成為體能心智皆強韌且有批判思考的自信少年，惟對現實世界的物質生活及社交生活皆一無所知。<br />\n<br />\n母親離世，虎爸一家決意到城市奔喪，滿足母親生前最後的遺願... 旅途程中滿是價值觀攻防戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/183703_db200da5118070978477db12b585a431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F183703_db200da5118070978477db12b585a431.jpg&h=d4da57f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSamantha Isler好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n簡單總結一下虎爸教育VS公共教育制度<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/183735_63c85d8fea3a65f4a0888e30607c53a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F183735_63c85d8fea3a65f4a0888e30607c53a7.jpg&h=6841056a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/29/183749_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F29%2F183749_75fbb7f751dcbed3164815928ce30210.jpg&h=b6072d40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劇情中，虎爸教出黎既大仔可以入曬全球所有頂級學府成為人類食物鍊頂層，但子女思想偏激之餘反建制，不時會用自己方式越過法律達成目標，可以話，如果全部人都係咁行事，只會令社會動盪。但於現世中，如此教育的確能激發子女所有潛能，自我實現，成為社會精英。<br />\n<br />\n爸絲們又點睇套電影？"},{"pid":"e77e3d7b27d08bee57d4a4410dfb889eff90ab63","tid":99608,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:23:43.000Z","msg":"邊到有得睇"},{"pid":"90ac94f824c56ce366775e18ce2aa19492f3c886","tid":99608,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"睇左, 其實我覺得虎爸某程度都係怪獸家長<br />\n不過喜劇就算la<br />\n但總括來說, 係幾好睇"},{"pid":"48f3286a32f76166e7e1e742edd1a75da0160657","tid":99608,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T11:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊到有得睇</blockquote><br />\n電影中心仲有上緊一兩場<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/details/9389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinema.com.hk%2Ftc%2Fmovie%2Fdetails%2F9389&d=UwQMSjbS41QxOfoXNLYtBRpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=5d30ab68\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cinema.com.hk/tc/movie/details/9389</a>"},{"pid":"1462b0130d8d25d3c5dc6d4e79cc60046e44e911","tid":99608,"uid":66182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r